Honey braised gochujang chicken and chickpeas! #BushsBeansPartner Step aside for this dreamy one-pan dinner. The most amazing gochujang sauce, braised to perfection and topped with lime juice. Pizza with smoked tomato sauce, loads of garlic and cherry tomatoes using my @ninjakitchen Woodfire Outdoor Oven! Garlicky and smoky tomatoes are so good here, then finished with mozzarella cheese, fresh basil, and colorful cherry tomatoes. First I smoked the tomatoes and garlic (blended to make a sauce) then switched to the Neapolitan pizza setting that gets up to 700 degrees to cook my no-turn pizza on the included stone (pizza cooked to perfection in 3 mins, hello!) You can shop the #NinjaOutdoorOven in my bio! 

The smoked tomato sauce is v easy: 6 large tomatoes, halved 1 head of garlic, halved 1/4 cup extra-virgin olive oil Kosher salt and freshly cracked black pepper 
Smoked for 30 mins, tomato skins removed and then blended. #SponsoredByNinja #NinjaWoodfire
